This paper discusses the development and challenges of federated learning systems, which involves machine learning models and privacy-preserving approaches. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
